==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Waybill
<hw>Way"bill`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A list of passengers
in a public vehicle, or of the baggage or gods transported by a common
carrier on a land route. When the goods are transported by water, the
list is called a <xex>bill of lading</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Waybread</ent>⟦br⟧
